name: Birdevo #142
description: Birdevo ( Bird Evolution ) is a 1234 AI and computerized generative NFT art with a bird as the main character. The reason behind this NFT is because forests continue to be cut down and bird habitat is decreasing. This NFT art supports a reforestation project to bring back bird habitat. In short, Birdevo is an adventure story about a group of birds who want to bring back their habitat using the power of blockchain.
